  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They let us in, and the next day, it was the German with the Ukraine, surrounded the place, I mean the forest, and they started to shoot.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were inside, and they started to shoot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they killed a lot of people that time, because a lot of people were in the forest, and they didn't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were running from one place to the other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were killed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were inside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But while-- during the day, my sister felt nauseous, and [NON-ENGLISH], the other friend, said, why do I have to stay here and die here?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll go out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let them kill me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's it, let us out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we opened-- opened the cover, and we let her out, [NON-ENGLISH] and my sister.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we heard the shooting all over, and I was sure that they were killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But when it stopped after a few hours, maybe the day it lasted, then it stopped.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we went out, because we felt ourselves that we are not able to breathe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we find them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were somewhere in a stack of hay.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, they were covered over, and they were alive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So since then, since this incident, so I told my sister, you know, we won't stay here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I-- I-- I don't like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because they don't want us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's-- it's no use.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We are in danger anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were dressed differently, as I told you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were walking in the same village, and we came to a house, a poor house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we came in, and they decided to take us in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And naturally, to cover us somewhere in the top of the attic.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
